"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*1Eb6lQbdwk2qSCLEe_DF7w.png)\\n\\n## “WePiggy’s Billionaires” on Polygon\\n\\nIn order to encourage users to participate in WePiggy-Polygon lending protocol, “WePiggy’s Billionaires” activity is now open!\\n\\n**Activity time:**2021/7/3 15:00(UTC+8) to WePiggy’s official launch on the next public chain or layer 2 network\\n\\n**Activity Rules:**\\n\\nDuring the activity, participate in WePiggy-Polygon WPC mining campaign, and the cumulative amount of mined WPC tokens ranks in the top **198** of the “WePiggy’s Billionaires”, will win the \\\\[Polygon Co-branded Edition\\\\] \\\\[Epic Level\\\\] NFT — “**MagicPiggy**”.\\n\\n**Please note:**\\n\\n1\\\\. The “MagicPiggy” NFT will be open for claim after the activity ends. Except for participating in this activity, or through the transfer of old holders in the future, no more “MagicPiggy” will be generated.\\n\\n2\\\\. WePiggy reserves the right of final interpretation of this activity.\\n\\n## Participation Tutorial\\n\\n## About “MagicPiggy” NFT\\n\\nThis card is issued to commemorate the third step of WePiggy’s cross-chain deployment plan: Polygon.\\n\\nRecite magical India mantras, open up a mysterious path connecting the DeFi world. Holder of this NFT will be blessed by WePiggy with the buff of “Magic Network, Connecting the DeFi World”.\",\"timestamp\":1636596521,\"title\":\"“WePiggy’s Billionaires” WPC Mining Competition on Polygon Begins！\"},\"digest\":\"vDQ61uqqx1IL-DrPgk5Mlix7k654iKaGF7JUe2VAzbY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MOToXuaua0SJZ5_SQSsecHvAOLw5KxmLTKhH_Amk1Lw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eHu9Uej8BHwgyRn4jxCzG9EQ1R29cSjilBrFY8fm7pw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Zy20hp1G2k-mspaO9VTIfDxsq0aedxCS59o_7lrCcz1NSispxt7w0paOwdoB8G1uUb0XJfDGirkSQLtUtgnDOw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0